Title : Okeover Inlet
Text : '''Okeover Inlet''', formerly '''Okeover Arm''',<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/45148.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Okeover Arm"]</ref> is an [[inlet]] in the [[Sunshine Coast (British Columbia)|Sunshine Coast]] region of the southwestern mainland of [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]].  It is the upper end of [[Malaspina Inlet]] and is northwest of [[Powell River, British Columbia|the City of Powell River]].<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/18003.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Okeover Inlet"]</ref>  [[Larsons Landing]], a steamer landing, is located on its eastern shore.<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/38216.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Larsons Landing (steamer landing)"]</ref>

[[Okeover Arm Provincial Park]] is located on its western shore.<ref>[http://www.env.gov.bc.ca/bcparks/explore/parkpgs/okeover/ BC Parks infopage]</ref><ref>{{BCGNIS|18000|Okeover Arm Park}}</ref>

